Hello, I'm the Nostalgia Critic! I remember it so YOU don't have to!

00:00:08.680 --> 00:00:11.400
And welcome to another installment of: "Was That Real?"

00:00:17.380 --> 00:00:22.480
Not utilizing an incredibly popular icon is like not utilizing an incredibly convenient cameo.

00:00:22.480 --> 00:00:24.000
Hey, you got any water around here?

00:00:24.000 --> 00:00:26.340
[Angry Video Game Nerd] Ohhhh, you want some WATER, yeah?

