Uh, so yeah. We're taking one more week on this review,

00:10:52.760 --> 00:10:56.100
but it'll definitely show... uh, in the final product,

00:10:56.100 --> 00:10:58.220
uh, so look forward to that!

00:10:58.220 --> 00:11:05.320
