00:11:15.720 --> 00:11:21.320
EVERYONE should have access to free, clean water. That is VITAL as what you need to survive,

00:11:21.580 --> 00:11:28.080
and... it's basically like being punished because of where you were born, not having something that essential.

00:11:28.080 --> 00:11:31.980
And this charity goes and they get clean water to these people.

00:11:31.980 --> 00:11:37.520
