00:11:46.180 --> 00:11:51.360
to help raise awareness and raise money and show support for this wonderful cause.

00:11:51.360 --> 00:11:55.480
And it's something that's going on right now, and you can go to their website...

00:11:55.480 --> 00:11:58.460
and check it out, and you can see what you can do.

00:11:58.460 --> 00:12:04.080
It's a wonderful chance to do just ALL sorts of various options to raise awareness of this...

00:12:04.080 --> 00:12:09.460
and the money all goes to getting water to people that really, really need it.

00:12:09.460 --> 00:12:14.000
That just need good, clean water to survive to live and to be healthy.

00:12:14.000 --> 00:12:20.560
It's the most vital thing you need! It's what we ALL need, and this is a charity that's trying to get it to everybody.

00:12:20.560 --> 00:12:26.600
So please, if you have a chance, definitely go check out this website, and see if you can show them your support.

